}

### 4. Delete Teacher Account (Replace {teacherId} with actual ID from step 2)
### (Replace {adminToken} with token from step 3)
DELETE http://localhost:5166/api/Account/{teacherId}
Authorization: Bearer {adminToken}

### 5. Test delete non-existent account
DELETE http://localhost:5166/api/Account/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {adminToken}

